This implementation focuses on Automated Data Sanitization & PII Masking, a critical real-world task for data engineers and privacy officers. The agent must identify sensitive information (Names, Emails, SSNs, Credit Cards) in raw datasets and apply the correct masking or redaction transformations while maintaining data utility
